'''Eden Consolidated Independent School District''' is a public [[school district]] based in [[Eden, Texas|Eden]], [[Texas]] ([[United States|USA]]).

The district is located in southern [[Concho County, Texas|Concho County]] and extends into a small portion of northern [[Menard County, Texas|Menard County]].

Eden Consolidated ISD has two campuses - Eden High (Grades 7-12) and Eden Elementary (Grades K-6).

